1097,/Hotel_Review-g186338-d11621939-Reviews-or1095-Novotel_London_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html#REVIEWS,Novotel London Canary Wharf Hotel Reviews,"Exciting new-build hotel, great restaurant and bars, superb views, and amazing staff","I stayed here February 14th, on business, not for Valentine's.  Overall I had a great experience and will likely stay here again.  The staff are unbelievably friendly and come across as really excited to work in this new space.  The rooms are new, clean, reasonably spacious - not palatial but decent.    I had dinner in the restaurant, beef tartar starter followed by the lobster.  The beef was good but the lobster was superb, one of the most tender I've ever tasted.  The restaurant and bar are on floor 37, 38 and 39, with panoramic views of both the nearby towers of Canary Wharf and the London skyline a few miles away.  Again, staff were super attentive and friendly.  A few points to note: this hotel is brand new and there are still a few teething issues they are working through.‚Ä¶",Date of stay: February 2017,5.0
